--- /dev/null
+++ b/packages/libtool/2.5.4/0004-Allow-statically-linking-Flang-support-libraries-whe.patch
@@ -0,0 +1,27 @@
+[PATCH] Allow statically linking Flang support libraries when linking
+  a library
